race.comment: DIVINE SOURCE (4) was a close-up fourth in a small field at Doomben fresh in a richer race than this. Fitter and worth following up. ANCIENT SCENT (1) broke through for an effortless maiden win last time out on the Gold Coast. Has upside and is at peak fitness. Low draw and can measure up again. MUSIC FEVER (8) has been knocking on the door with seconds at her last two starts. Has a low draw and gets a chance. LADY ALABAMA (13) is rarely far away and has won two of her last five. Winner two back at Grafton and would go close on best figures. I'LLTELLYOUSO (7) made progress finishing midfield last start at Warwick on a soft track, could add some value to betting.
